text: Dardanelle is a city in Yell County, Arkansas, United States. It is near Lake Dardanelle. The population was 4,517 at the 2020 census. Along with Danville, it is one of two county seats for Yell County. ==References== ==Other websites== * Dardanelle Chamber of Commerce * City of Dardanelle Arkansas Portal style website, Government, Business, Library, Recreation and more * City-Data.com Comprehensive Statistical Data and more about Dardanelle Category:Cities in Arkansas Category:County seats in Arkansas
